data.description: Welcome to your next home in the highly sought-after Moore School District! This immaculate 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence offers a perfect blend of modern comfort and classic charm. Nestled in a friendly neighborhood, this property is an ideal place to create lasting memories. Living in the prestigious Williamson Farms community offers a wealth of amenities, including a community pool, parks, and walking trails. Neighborhood also offers easy access to I-44 with nearby parks, shopping centers, and dining options.
